{"tid":1678644,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲試過成功曬黑","createTime":"2019-10-27T18:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T09:32:12.000Z","uid":171745,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2315f3bb52bbe86a1bbe2051ad79fb599d8ef8c5","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"真心求教，雖然話一白遮三醜<br />\n但年紀漸大就覺得黑先係健康膚色<br />\n<br />\n自己少少白低，後生啲時都係盲目追美白用好多護膚品希望保持perfect白<br />\n但天生皮膚唔係好好果種，點都有啲礙眼位，<br />\n一白就好覺好似好唔精神咁<br />\n見到啲少少黑嘅女仔好似皮膚唔洗好perfect個感覺都睇落好健康<br />\n有做開運動，試過想曬黑<br />\n但一曬就又甩皮又剩，搽野又紅又生暗瘡之類<br />\n好快又白返<br />\n<br />\n身邊有變黑成功嘅都好似係男仔<br />\n有冇絲試過成功變黑<br />\n真係好想有cheronna / 瑞瑪席丹嘅膚色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2d63a368274ef8b0728ab1c4b13a8fa65e77ab","tid":1678644,"uid":132655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"落啲防曬，防曬好似有講究話邊隻成份係防曬黑，邊隻係防曬傷。做完運動完買支蘆薈曬後gel搽下，好少會甩皮。有排工作需要成日要跑戶外，做足上述措施未試過曬甩皮，不過就黑過朱凱迪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好羨慕絲打白底，小妹曬一曬好耐先白返<br />\n<br />\n利申非敏感肌，不過蘆薈曬後gel應該都對敏感肌友好"},{"pid":"93e374aa71bb2c8af1291942044a2fbd2947b720","tid":1678644,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T22:23:44.000Z","msg":"我都想健康地曬黑<br />\n其實雖然我依加黑咗，但只係因為成日唔搽防晒走去戶外同埋出汗啲防曬就甩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991025ccc99e856f1e62ff0d848bdd0ec0163f29","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93e374aa71bb2c8af1291942044a2fbd2947b720","tid":1678644,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T22:23:44.000Z","msg":"我都想健康地曬黑<br />\n其實雖然我依加黑咗，但只係因為成日唔搽防晒走去戶外同埋出汗啲防曬就甩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:30:44.000Z","msg":"我搽防曬只會少啲曬傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我無論點特登去曬都會有種皮膚抵擋唔住嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前聽人講要搽黑鬼油先會變黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買過一支覺得搽同唔搽完全冇分別就冇再試<br />\n已經試左一兩年户外活動都唔係好work 重曬到有啲黄黄地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有輪見到ROLA 咁黑黑地金髮好正<br />\n唔通真係要試下做燈？"},{"pid":"30925f8d469051daa702aafc16d7eb56df3de037","tid":1678644,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:31:11.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽 5毛大軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=289b1143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"82c090ca78354ec455d77625c68f9784c044061e","tid":1678644,"uid":21197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"會曬傷嘅人好難曬黑 我諗要長期暴露係陽光底下先得<br />\n利申黑底 好羨慕啲皮膚勁白嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e119c673c4a66663860f5d77edfbe3712246188","tid":1678644,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:33:46.000Z","msg":"絲打你本身係好白既?<br />\n<br />\n我男朋友佢本身好撚白 又係一曬就甩皮 就算唔甩皮都紅到仆街<br />\n我就相反 曬一曬就好易黑<br />\n然後佢KEEP住跟我曬 搽黑鬼油 依家都開始成功黑到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafb3c816581c1877d3cd6d7d539865c842196b8","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c2d63a368274ef8b0728ab1c4b13a8fa65e77ab","tid":1678644,"uid":132655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"落啲防曬，防曬好似有講究話邊隻成份係防曬黑，邊隻係防曬傷。做完運動完買支蘆薈曬後gel搽下，好少會甩皮。有排工作需要成日要跑戶外，做足上述措施未試過曬甩皮，不過就黑過朱凱迪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好羨慕絲打白底，小妹曬一曬好耐先白返<br />\n<br />\n利申非敏感肌，不過蘆薈曬後gel應該都對敏感肌友好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:34:17.000Z","msg":"我接近係完全相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 敏感肌+曬唔黑<br />\n睇黎真係隔離飯香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過真係唔知防曬有分防曬傷同曬黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以研究下，之前一係就用運動型防水果啲，一係就用返平時用開啲護膚brands (自己就用cetaphil / DHC 果啲）"},{"pid":"388a649ce879a31345f7b1886f9e83cebc2d5dc2","tid":1678644,"uid":300164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"我反而想變白<br />\n細細個游完水就曬黑到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白唔翻"},{"pid":"7f14d4577ba95d50bdcb3ad7257aac06cef1a66c","tid":1678644,"uid":211449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:35:56.000Z","msg":"曬黑真係好撚正"},{"pid":"89107c8a722d8ebcb0852f55d87c643a1639f0ad","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"388a649ce879a31345f7b1886f9e83cebc2d5dc2","tid":1678644,"uid":300164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"我反而想變白<br />\n細細個游完水就曬黑到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白唔翻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:36:52.000Z","msg":"我細個游左好多年水都係黑唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b142002775bc43dbdfae8a9f158b64b2f27f50ce","tid":1678644,"uid":165339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:38:45.000Z","msg":"不要說黑,試著說小麥膚色/運動型膚色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f012e3deccd2e4f14f40429d4f4d481d1d757620","tid":1678644,"uid":160277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:39:10.000Z","msg":"一直都好中意黑黑地嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚正"},{"pid":"55d6e76624ddb756b68b96fb5b2434b9814035f7","tid":1678644,"uid":207990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:39:22.000Z","msg":"有無例子圖"},{"pid":"0cd9b05fb4db040399af827d8c6fea937387a208","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f012e3deccd2e4f14f40429d4f4d481d1d757620","tid":1678644,"uid":160277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:39:10.000Z","msg":"一直都好中意黑黑地嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚正"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"引左好多小麥色絲入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時得到答案係同老豆會唔會買樓比自己一樣<br />\n天生好唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bbe262beb454831063d77735a6aad6fc5d77ee","tid":1678644,"uid":132655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bafb3c816581c1877d3cd6d7d539865c842196b8","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c2d63a368274ef8b0728ab1c4b13a8fa65e77ab","tid":1678644,"uid":132655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"落啲防曬，防曬好似有講究話邊隻成份係防曬黑，邊隻係防曬傷。做完運動完買支蘆薈曬後gel搽下，好少會甩皮。有排工作需要成日要跑戶外，做足上述措施未試過曬甩皮，不過就黑過朱凱迪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好羨慕絲打白底，小妹曬一曬好耐先白返<br />\n<br />\n利申非敏感肌，不過蘆薈曬後gel應該都對敏感肌友好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:34:17.000Z","msg":"我接近係完全相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 敏感肌+曬唔黑<br />\n睇黎真係隔離飯香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過真係唔知防曬有分防曬傷同曬黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以研究下，之前一係就用運動型防水果啲，一係就用返平時用開啲護膚brands (自己就用cetaphil / DHC 果啲）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.medpartner.club/sunscreen-spa-pa-boots-star/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medpartner.club%2Fsunscreen-spa-pa-boots-star%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=002a8cfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.medpartner.club/sunscreen-spa-pa-boots-star/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢篇簡單易理解少少，絲打個情況可能要搵支SPF強嘅防曬傷，隔兩個鐘就補一補。同埋曬後蘆薈gel真係唔少得，曬完唔補水鎮靜好難唔甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講開呢樣，有無巴絲用過啲噴霧型防曬，好似好方便咁但其實有無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27d10a431784cfe16731e93f605b4bac6d03f55","tid":1678644,"uid":132655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cd9b05fb4db040399af827d8c6fea937387a208","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f012e3deccd2e4f14f40429d4f4d481d1d757620","tid":1678644,"uid":160277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:39:10.000Z","msg":"一直都好中意黑黑地嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚正"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"引左好多小麥色絲入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時得到答案係同老豆會唔會買樓比自己一樣<br />\n天生好唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"同埋睇身型，瘦仲要黑嘅話，人地會以為屋企虐待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac76df4bd0ca24011faa27dbfc28bd10fb3bf20","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37bbe262beb454831063d77735a6aad6fc5d77ee","tid":1678644,"uid":132655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bafb3c816581c1877d3cd6d7d539865c842196b8","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c2d63a368274ef8b0728ab1c4b13a8fa65e77ab","tid":1678644,"uid":132655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"落啲防曬，防曬好似有講究話邊隻成份係防曬黑，邊隻係防曬傷。做完運動完買支蘆薈曬後gel搽下，好少會甩皮。有排工作需要成日要跑戶外，做足上述措施未試過曬甩皮，不過就黑過朱凱迪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好羨慕絲打白底，小妹曬一曬好耐先白返<br />\n<br />\n利申非敏感肌，不過蘆薈曬後gel應該都對敏感肌友好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:34:17.000Z","msg":"我接近係完全相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 敏感肌+曬唔黑<br />\n睇黎真係隔離飯香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過真係唔知防曬有分防曬傷同曬黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以研究下，之前一係就用運動型防水果啲，一係就用返平時用開啲護膚brands (自己就用cetaphil / DHC 果啲）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.medpartner.club/sunscreen-spa-pa-boots-star/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medpartner.club%2Fsunscreen-spa-pa-boots-star%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=002a8cfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.medpartner.club/sunscreen-spa-pa-boots-star/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢篇簡單易理解少少，絲打個情況可能要搵支SPF強嘅防曬傷，隔兩個鐘就補一補。同埋曬後蘆薈gel真係唔少得，曬完唔補水鎮靜好難唔甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講開呢樣，有無巴絲用過啲噴霧型防曬，好似好方便咁但其實有無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:59:03.000Z","msg":"有用過一輪，唔知係咪唔識噴，感覺冇搽咁有效"},{"pid":"c090fea480d016e5554ccec2ee0c45ffe0f736b2","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55d6e76624ddb756b68b96fb5b2434b9814035f7","tid":1678644,"uid":207990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:39:22.000Z","msg":"有無例子圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:16:31.000Z","msg":"曬傷例子圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37ab269dee4284db8f26103525e11dcc940dffb","tid":1678644,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:17:05.000Z","msg":"串撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ca23107da0d0f98a511373c3ad10dac352dc7d","tid":1678644,"uid":232460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:17:31.000Z","msg":"師兄有冇興趣跟我去游水？"},{"pid":"d25229d33c7e64ea9d2afa6d67c62bf2a730b805","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d37ab269dee4284db8f26103525e11dcc940dffb","tid":1678644,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:17:05.000Z","msg":"串撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"真心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ac1a4b26c0614f208ea990b2d0859a71db5881","tid":1678644,"uid":92881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2315f3bb52bbe86a1bbe2051ad79fb599d8ef8c5","tid":1678644,"uid":171745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"真心求教，雖然話一白遮三醜<br />\n但年紀漸大就覺得黑先係健康膚色<br />\n<br />\n自己少少白低，後生啲時都係盲目追美白用好多護膚品希望保持perfect白<br />\n但天生皮膚唔係好好果種，點都有啲礙眼位，<br />\n一白就好覺好似好唔精神咁<br />\n見到啲少少黑嘅女仔好似皮膚唔洗好perfect個感覺都睇落好健康<br />\n有做開運動，試過想曬黑<br />\n但一曬就又甩皮又剩，搽野又紅又生暗瘡之類<br />\n好快又白返<br />\n<br />\n身邊有變黑成功嘅都好似係男仔<br />\n有冇絲試過成功變黑<br />\n真係好想有cheronna / 瑞瑪席丹嘅膚色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"我白底成功曬黑<br />\n好多人話我黑左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心得： 好天就出去曬 唔懶得 但都要防曬 可以用防曬+tanning oil/有防曬系數嘅tanning oil"},{"pid":"11e97c00662be3551a3ccceaacf61895b125865e","tid":1678644,"uid":327316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:47:01.000Z","msg":"黑鬼油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年結婚無得曬<br />\n以前曬黑睇落仲會瘦左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2f27dc710d6a33f8df2e7206a8be6d8706566b","tid":1678644,"uid":173850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:48:58.000Z","msg":"黑好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}